Package: corMLPE
Title: A correlation structure for symmetric relational data 
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Nathaniel", "Pope", email = "nspope@utexas.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package implements a correlation structure for symmetric relational data (e.g. pairwise distances, dissimilarities) that interfaces with the nlme package (and anything else that can use a nlme-like correlation structure). 
Imports:
    Rcpp (>= 0.12.7),
    nlme,
    MASS
Depends:
    nlme,
    MASS
License: GPL
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
